1.problem:rtools can not work

solution:install.packages("devtools")
         install.packages("installr")
         install.packages("stringr")
         library(stringr)
         library(installr)
         install.Rtools()
		 
2.problem:install.packages("Rcpp")
failed to lock directory 'D:/R/R-3.6.3/library' for modifying

solution: find the file in 'D:/R/R-3.6.3/library/00LOCK-Rcpp',and deleteit it,then install again

3.problem:due to the SHA1 (0f392995) has not changed since last install so the code devtools::install_github("hadley/sloop") can not work
 
solution : devtools::install_github("hadley/sloop",force = TRUE)

